{"tid":2029890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港版國安法]美國務卿揚言與香港人同一陣線 譴責北京並要重新考慮","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T21:06:52.000Z","uid":278767,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7f88c8a69225906c4ac07bb4cb8864450325f9aa","tid":2029890,"uid":278767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200522/NJYELGR5GBEW5JOTDUWT4WVUTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200522%2FNJYELGR5GBEW5JOTDUWT4WVUTY%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=e49098bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200522%2FNJYELGR5GBEW5JOTDUWT4WVUTY%2F&h=dbf0ba7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200522/NJYELGR5GBEW5JOTDUWT4WVUTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大會議擬繞過香港立法程序，將港版國安法納入《基本法》附件三形式直接在港實施，震驚國際。美國國務卿蓬佩奧發表聲明譴責，揚言美國與香港人站在同一陣線，強烈要求北京重新考慮其「災難性建議」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在聲明中表示，中共政府決定繞過香港的立法程序及忽視港人的意願，將為聯合聲明承諾的自治「敲響喪鐘」。他更強調任何損害香港自治的決定，「將無可避免地影響我們對一國兩制及地區狀況的評估」。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜發言人則表示，正密切注視香港的局勢，期望中國尊重香港的權利和自由，及英國向香港承諾的自治權。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\nApp內1-Click訂閱《蘋果動新聞》"},{"pid":"ec6bd56ace83d7e31e0adebbf6659ba6420c5645","tid":2029890,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"df75ade6665fc3cebca44f046714b8702007e4d2","tid":2029890,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜發言人則表示，正密切注視香港的局勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cbeead9bfb81cf96bce2843761eff71eed248f","tid":2029890,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"日落帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c40a1a1cdb106f5178bc867953567288dab51a9","tid":2029890,"uid":175731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"其實英國可以唔洗再出聲如果只係得呢幾句，你既觀望心意香港人都收到了。"},{"pid":"871c3dc94c10fbd50e3b55ba0e61059ed71dddec","tid":2029890,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df75ade6665fc3cebca44f046714b8702007e4d2","tid":2029890,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜發言人則表示，正密切注視香港的局勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"佢肺炎上腦"},{"pid":"35fce735162489f6a5733ad3ef5700d68f70497c","tid":2029890,"uid":1990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df75ade6665fc3cebca44f046714b8702007e4d2","tid":2029890,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜發言人則表示，正密切注視香港的局勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"一直關注事件 天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be33f7cb35b6bd1e0eeca591afee303a83ed2d36","tid":2029890,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:36:24.000Z